in the admin page, the "more..." in the logs section should always be accessible.

### actual behaviour
parts of the "more..." button are drawn behind the currently hovered log line.

### steps to reproduce
1. try to press the more... button

### server configuration
operating system: centos 6 

web server: apache httpd 2.2.15

database: sqlite 3.6.20

php version: 5.3.3

owncloud version: 5.0.0-rc1

### client configuration
